        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "text": "Magnesium"
        }
      ],
      "correct_choice_id": 1,
      "solution": "<p><strong>Correct Answer: B) Selenium</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>Explanation</strong>:</p>\n\n<p>Selenium (Se) is an essential <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"e3ae50eb0b1692777192c2315d2da8\">micronutrient</span> for an <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"1f3c08447d16927771819ccd566468\">antioxidant</span> defence that integrates an important part of selenoproteins.</p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>The most well-known selenoproteins are five <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"f945849e691692777188ad7ce5b5e2\">glutathione</span> peroxidases (GPx), which protect cells from damage caused by free radicals such as <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"092583d1b41692777197a506409267\">reactive</span> oxygen species (ROS).</li>\n\t<li>Reduce <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"a99114a6c216927771916f45ffc66c\">lipid</span> hydroperoxides to their corresponding alcohols and to reduce free <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"11f7bcb8da16927771898e93932195\">hydrogen</span> <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"7e35dc67351692777195c0be6eee0b\">peroxide</span> to water.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Manganese (Option A): </strong>Not the <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"a416d7580c1692777184952da793d1\">cofactor</span> for <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"f945849e691692777188ad7ce5b5e2\">glutathione</span> peroxidase.It is a <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"a416d7580c1692777184952da793d1\">cofactor</span> for <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"4903b2c802169277719110203f4af5\">manganese</span> <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"7d51964ce51692777199dedcf19fc3\">superoxide</span> dismutase, arginase, and <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"f9129e152d16927771960c4ccc40bc\">pyruvate</span> carboxylase.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Copper (Option C): </strong>Cofactor and regulator of copper, <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"39ecb6e07416927772029550b7e74a\">zinc</span> <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"7d51964ce51692777199dedcf19fc3\">superoxide</span> dismutase.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Magnesium (Option D): </strong>Cofactor in ATP-generating reactions.</p>",
