      "correct_choice_id": 1,
      "solution": "<p><strong>Correct Option B - Liver <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"754ab07a2e1692777183ed178c883d\">biopsy</span> for <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"7b5fb2b56416927771858f02fd5508\">copper</span> estimation</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>Explanation: </strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li><strong>Wilson’s Disease </strong>is characterized by excessive <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"7b5fb2b56416927771858f02fd5508\">copper</span> accumulation, particularly in the liver and brain, and the gold standard for diagnosis is a liver <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"754ab07a2e1692777183ed178c883d\">biopsy</span> with <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"ef5cb829b8169277719603304e73cb\">quantitative</span> <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"7b5fb2b56416927771858f02fd5508\">copper</span> estimation.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Inheritance </strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Autosomal recessive</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Gene </strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Mutation in <strong>ATP7B</strong> gene (chromosome 13)</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Defect </strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Impaired <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"7b5fb2b56416927771858f02fd5508\">copper</span> <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"0f7653c9ef1692777187deaa35f749\">excretion</span> into <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"cf978047b61692777183c0569f21f2\">bile</span> → <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"7b5fb2b56416927771858f02fd5508\">copper</span> accumulation in <strong>liver</strong>, <strong>brain</strong>, <strong>cornea</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Clinical features </strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Hepatic:</strong> Hepatitis, hepatomegaly, cirrhosis</p>\n\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Neurological:</strong> Tremors, dysarthria, dystonia, parkinsonism</p>\n\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Psychiatric:</strong> Behavioural changes, personality disorders</p>\n\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Ocular:</strong> <strong>Kayser-Fleischer rings</strong> (golden-brown ring at corneal limbus)</p>\n\n\t\t\t<p><img alt=\"\" data-author=\"\" data-hash=\"\" data-license=\"\" data-source=\"\" data-tags=\"\" height=\"4193\" src=\"https://image.prepladder.com/content/z5mGkPuQiMKb1WYoii0H1755853298.png\" width=\"5851\" /></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Diagnosis </strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>↓ Serum ceruloplasmin<strong> </strong><strong>(Option A ruled out)</strong></p>\n\n\t\t\t<p>↑ 24-hour <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"0b72f5e96b16927772018dec8a87e2\">urinary</span> <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"7b5fb2b56416927771858f02fd5508\">copper</span> excretion<strong> </strong><strong>(Option D ruled out)</strong></p>\n\n\t\t\t<p>↑ <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"3268e86ce01692777188f249c64d6e\">Hepatic</span> <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"7b5fb2b56416927771858f02fd5508\">copper</span> on liver <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"754ab07a2e1692777183ed178c883d\">biopsy</span> (gold standard) <strong>(Option B)</strong></p>\n\n\t\t\t<p><strong>MRI brain:</strong> Panda sign (in severe cases)</p>\n\n\t\t\t<p><img alt=\"\" data-author=\"\" data-hash=\"\" data-license=\"\" data-source=\"\" data-tags=\"\" height=\"5874\" src=\"https://image.prepladder.com/content/yMEnK00mE4mHFWMgB73m1755853304.png\" width=\"5543\" /></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Management </strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Chelation therapy:</strong> Penicillamine or Trientine</p>\n\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Zinc supplements:</strong> Inhibit <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"7b5fb2b56416927771858f02fd5508\">copper</span> absorption</p>\n\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Liver transplant:</strong> In <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"104c254ce81692777203458937f730\">fulminant</span> <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"3268e86ce01692777188f249c64d6e\">hepatic</span> failure</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p><br />\n<strong>Serum <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"7b5fb2b56416927771858f02fd5508\">copper</span> (Option C)</strong> is usually low, since most <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"7b5fb2b56416927771858f02fd5508\">copper</span> is ceruloplasmin-bound.</p>",
